
PiShop Online is changing the status quo of payments in Web3 via its online e-commerce platform. It is an online e-commerce platform for B2B and C2C sales which are entirely processed in Pi via the Pi browser.
Pi has shown great relevance in the Web3 community as a means of payment. The use of cryptocurrency is a new revolution in the history of money and at PiShop online, our major goal is to offer a diverse range of products at the best Pi price. While doing this, we are also standing as a means to connect sellers and brands who are Pi pioneers with millions of consumers globally.
